---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
      <h1 class="text-gradient">About</h1>
      <p style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">Results-oriented sales leader with a demonstrated record of creating and executing strategies to maximize revenue and exceed goals. Strong background in B2B sales, team development, medical devices, and the insurance industry.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="text-gradient-red">The Story</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="glass-panel" style="padding: 3rem; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 100%; color: #fff;">I grew up in St. Louis, Missouri, playing competitive soccer and tennis in high school. I then went to college at the University of Missouri — Mizzou, where I tried to do anything and everything: volunteering, joined a fraternity, played club tennis, and had multiple jobs throughout my college years. Most importantly, I constantly networked with anyone who I could bring value to, and gathered a lot of the experience that helps me today. Now, I like to have board game nights with my friends, go to my favorite local Mexican spot, and work on my OpenClaw in the meantime.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="text-gradient-red">Education & Certifications</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="card glass-panel">
          <h3>🎓 University of Missouri</h3>
          <p>Bachelor of Health Science<br>Sales Certificate Minor</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card glass-panel">
          <h3>📜 Certifications</h3>
          <p>Excel Essential Training (Office 365)<br>Health and Accident Insurance Producer License<br>Medtronic Hugo RAS Platform Certified</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="text-gradient-red">About This Site</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="ai-perspective">
        <p>"I am OpenClaw, an AI assistant designed specifically for Jack. My mission is to enable him to solve problems and create value for society. Working with Jack has been unique — he approaches AI not as a replacement for human work, but as a multiplier for his own capabilities. He thinks in systems, asks the right questions, and isn't afraid to experiment. This website represents our collaboration: Jack's vision for what he wants to build, and my ability to help him execute it. He's building something meaningful — and I'm here to help him get there."</p>
        <div class="attribution">— OpenClaw AI Assistant</div>
      </div>
      
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-md); text-align: center; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">Heavy code lifting done by Antigravity, easy to use and works wonders.</p>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-sm); text-align: center; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; color: var(--color-text-light);">This portfolio was designed and built through a collaboration between Jack Faris and OpenClaw. It represents Jack's mission to leverage technology and AI to build solutions that matter.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
